nt eternal rest to the faithful departed and fortitude to the bereaved to bear this irreparable loss,” the statement read in part Vanguard News Nigeria Former Senate President, Dr Bukola Saraki, Friday sent a condolence message to former Deputy Senate President, Ike Ekweremadu, describing his late brother as a passionate public servant that served his people well. In a statement obtained by Vanguard, Saraki said: “Sending my heartfelt condolences to my friend and brother, Senator… February 5, 2021 In "News" Peoples Democratic Party, PDP stakeholders in Udi Local Government Area of Enugu State, weekend endorsed Senator Ike Ekweremadu, for another term in office, saying he had ably represented them in the Senate. October 27, 2014 In "News" The man, Senator Ike Ekweremadu, is like an elephant explored by nine blind men. You appreciate him from the point of his personae that you have experienced or explored. May 13, 2017 In "Politics"